data.description: BACK on the MARKET!!!  Charming starter house in the heart of Altadena is brimming with potential. Nestled on 5,564 lot with a breathtaking mountain view from the backyard. Located on a private street. Perfect for first-time homebuyers or savvy investors, this property offers an entry-level price for the Altadena market. Perfectly located to walking distance to Loma Alta Park, minutes drive to JPL and Great Old Town Pasadena. Don't miss out on the chance to make this your dream home or a lucrative investment opportunity. Close to the Farmer's market, horse trails and  Altadena library. Get ready to seize this one-of-a-kind chance in Altadena!
